caption.title: The efficiency of HPX8C RNAi.
caption.p: HPX8C mRNA expression at 1 day PBM in mosquitoes carcass injected with dsEGFP or dsHPX8C. All experiments were repeated in triplicate. Student’s t-tests were used to determine the significance of difference in expression between treated and control groups. Data are represented as mean ± SEM. * p<0.05.
